text- align:center;"|Runners-up |- |colspan="3" style="background:#FFC0CB; text- align:center;"|Elimination |- |} The Star (season 11) () was the eleventh season of The Star, a singing competition produced by Exact, a GMM Grammy Company. Preliminary auditions took place during November to December, and broadcast on One HD, began on 17 January 2015.
